Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.18,0:00:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ataque!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.12,0:00:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Estrutura de Hoshijiro perdida!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Perda de contato com o piloto!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.99,0:00:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gaunas estão agora a menos de 2000 km de distância.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Como ele pode ter um canhão Heigus...?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.62,0:00:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}E um tão grande...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.00,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{bg}Você pode me ouvir, Tanikaze?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.83,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{bg}Recolha Honoka e Kunato e evacue a área imediatamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.70,0:00:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Essa luz vermelha pode ser um órgão de distribuição de Higgs, e se for...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.62,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Responda! Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.39,0:00:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze pegou o Kabizashi\Ne está se aproximando da Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.89,0:00:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,O que ele está planejando?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cumpra suas ordens, Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Reúna seus companheiros e evacuem!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.85,0:00:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A reação de Higgs dentro da Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo, Nagate?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Responda, Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.53,0:01:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gaunas dispararam seu canhão de partículas Heigus.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,O G487 perdeu grande parte da sua placenta!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Núcleo exposto!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele estava mirando uma explosão de interferência Heigus?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.38,0:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sem mudança de curso para o Gauna ou para a estrutura de Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Ele realmente...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,T menos 5 segundos até o contato.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}4...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.18,0:01:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}3...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}2...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}1...
