Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.67,0:03:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}É...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Desintegração da bolha G487 confirmada.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze derrotou os Gaunas.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze, você não está ferido?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.44,0:03:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum... Eu vou procurar por Hoshijiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, resgatem Kunato e Honoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Volte, Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, Tanikaze{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.40,0:03:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dano no quadro de Tanikaze: pesado.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Armazenamento de partículas Heigus baixo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.12,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, tenha cuidado.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze, se você for mais longe, você não conseguirá voltar para Sidônia!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.95,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sei a velocidade de Hoshijiro no momento em que ela fugiu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sem alteração na rota de Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele está prestes a cruzar o ponto sem retorno.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.55,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Tanikaze...]
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sei.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Link de comunicação cortado.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze cruzou o ponto sem retorno.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.02,0:04:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixo o resto com você.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Envie um esquadrão para recuperar Kunato e Honoka imediatamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tragam o esquadrão de defesa.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os quadros devem retornar.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A missão acabou.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os quadros devem retornar a Sidonia.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fim das operações.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os quadros devem retornar a Sidonia.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fim das operações.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá, Izana.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Nagate...]
