Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Você deve ter levado para os Garde rapidamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que você quis se tornar um piloto, Hoshijiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Por quê, de fato...{I don't know.}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que esqueci.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.76,0:11:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Nada.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cara, eu tô com tanta fome.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos coletando Partículas Heigus bem devagar.
