Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oito dias, hein?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.53,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fnZekton\blur5\alpha&H50&\fs15\frz3.043\fax0.02\c&HCFF9AF&\pos(541.5,187)}Oito Dias Desde o Início do Sistema
