Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Não está saindo água.{Why's the water not coming out?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve, Tanikaze{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Não está saindo água.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda deveria sobrar um pouco.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.51,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A balança está presa\Nonde estava ontem.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.51,0:17:21.97,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnZekton\b1\blur0.5\fs19\bord2\fax0.07\fry350\c&H4A4C51&\3c&H4A4C51&\pos(505,228)\frz340}Erro
