Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.89,0:17:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Talvez o sensor do tanque de água esteja danificado.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos mudar para o sensor auxiliar.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vazio?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.06,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Como?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Oh, não...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Como está, Tanikaze{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sem esperança.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Foi perfurado.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Mas...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.20,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Não há mais água nem comida.
