Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho água.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Abra a boca.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Beba agora.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0!]
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Calma.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Beba devagar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Como você está se sentindo?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro, filtração!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,O lubrificante dos Gardes contém água, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles... contêm.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Talvez a gente consiga filtrar isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.30,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos tentar!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.72,0:19:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Não creio que alguém já tenha tentado filtrar esse lubrificante.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.86,0:19:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0!]
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Não morra por mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.67,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Você conseguiu, Tanikaze{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Água! Temos água, Hoshijiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Tanikaze[T2]...]
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshijiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,São esses os Garde?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uau.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.51,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,256 quadros em propulsão reversa.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles vieram atrás de nós!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.89,0:20:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Viva!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.01,0:20:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos sobreviver!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmissão do esquadrão de retransmissão.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.06,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Demorou demais.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Coloque na tela principal.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.11,0:21:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Localizamos Tanikaze Nagate\Ne Hoshijiro Shizuka.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.61,0:21:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Não creio que o braço de defesa da nave\Njá tenha feito uma mutina coletiva.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.58,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Você sabe que\Nvocê será punido?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Totalmente.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelos céus.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.79,0:21:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Por ordens suas, Capitã.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.05,0:21:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sidônia parece ter 257 celas de prisão para você?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que você sabe o que eu quero dizer.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.47,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,É só isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.97,0:21:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Sinceramente...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.49,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.20,0:21:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá, herói.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Herói?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.66,0:21:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou te dar um jeito depois.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.08,0:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho bastante água\Naqui comigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou brincando.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.25,0:22:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare de tagarelar, agente 007.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.71,0:22:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.05,0:22:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos voltar para Sidônia.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os quadros, potência máxima.
